                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nA residual limb sock must be worn at all times to absorb perspiration and is changed daily. The residual limb is washed, dried, and inspected for breakdown twice each day. The socket of the prosthesis is cleansed with a mild detergent and rinsed and dried carefully each day. A harsh bactericidal agent would not be used.\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nFocus on the subject, skin care after amputation to prevent breakdown. Eliminate options 1 and 3 because of the extended time frames. Eliminate option 4 because of the word harsh.",
